An '''assault gunboat''' was a type of [[gunboat]] that was used by the [[Imperial Navy|naval forces]] of the [[Galactic Empire]]<ref name="Dawn">''[[Dawn of Rebellion]]''</ref> and other parties.<ref name="BMF 99">{{BuildFalconCite|99|Starship Fact File}}</ref> [[Imperial I-class Star Destroyer|''Imperial I''-class Star Destroyers]] carried five of this type of gunboat<ref name="BMF 23">{{BuildFalconCite|23|Starship Fact File}}</ref> and [[Death Star's fleet]] was composed of hundreds of [[starship]]s, that ranged from [[dreadnought]]s to assault gunboats.<ref name="Dawn" /> The [[SS-54 assault ship]] was a class of assault gunboat that was mistakenly registered as a [[light freighter]].<ref name="BMF 99" />

